# stack.env — Portainer requires this file to exist for Git-based Stacks.
#
# Real values are set in Portainer UI:
#   Stack > Environment variables > Add env var
# UI values override anything set here.
#
# Required keys (referenced by compose.prod.yaml):
#
#   POSTGRES_DB             e.g. iknos
#   POSTGRES_USER           e.g. iknos
#   POSTGRES_PASSWORD       (strong, generated)
#
#   TRAEFIK_NETWORK         name of the external Traefik docker network on this host
#   API_DOMAIN              public hostname, e.g. iknos.example.com
#   TRAEFIK_ENTRYPOINT      Traefik entrypoint (default: websecure)
#   TRAEFIK_CERT_RESOLVER   Traefik cert resolver (default: letsencrypt)
#
# Optional:
#
#   LOG_LEVEL               default: INFO
#   BACKUP_RETAIN           how many sql.gz dumps to keep (default: 14)
